nderstand and easy to learn.<br></li><li> Character Customization<br>Customize the playable characters with a variety of costumes.<br></li><li> Interesting story and perspective<br>The story is full of fun with an original perspective.<br></li><li> Guest Characters<br>There are guest characters from my other games to help you out in the game.</li></ul>",
